íŸ@277578860cc6b2cf521ef8e9d8762b45ea8f2aca4b8e554ab0d75fd1c012aeb2⁄ÅTitle: title: polars is-not-null
Path: Examples
Content:
Create mask where values are not null
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> let s = ([5 6 0 8] | polars into-df);
    let res = ($s / $s);
    $res | polars is-not-null
